data.description:
THE ONE YOU HAVE BEEN WAITNG FOR....Discover the awesomeness of waterfront living in this lovely two-story
townhouse. With a thoughtfully designed layout, the primary bedroom graces the downstairs providing convenience
& privacy. Sunlight floods through ample windows illuminating the stylish interior. The heart of this home is its
updated kitchen, a culinary haven featuring a breakfast bar that seamlessly combines style & functionality. Ascend
the staircase to discover an added dimension of comfort-a loft upstairs, creating a versatile space adjacent to two
bedrooms. The allure extends beyond the interior-an expensive deck becomes an outdoor haven for entertaining or
simply savoring the peaceful moments by the water. The dock & boathouse open doors to water adventures, creating
a lifestyle where every day feels like a vacation. Very short boat ride to our beautiful Lake Pontchartrain. Embrace
the magic of the boat parades as they gracefully glide behind your home becoming an integral part of the distinctive
& vibrant lifestyle offered by this residence. Just a short drive away to explore the rich culture of New Orleans or
unwind on the Mississippi Gulf Coast. This is not just a home, it’s an invitation to a lifestyle of unparalleled waterfront
living. DON'T DELAY, CALL TODAY!
